resources.string: "Ngemuva kokususa umsebenzisi osele wale moto, umsebenzisi omusha womlawuli uzodalwa."
"Yonke idatha, izilungiselelo, kanye nezinhlelo zokusebenza eziphathelene nalo msebenzisi kuzosuswa. Uzodinga ukusetha isistimu futhi."
"Udinga okungenani umlawuli oyedwa. Ukuze ususe lo, qala ngokukhetha ukumiselela."

"Lokhu kuzosebenzisa idatha, kodwa uzodinga ukuvumelanisa i-akhawunti ngayinye ukuze uqoqe ulwazi lwakamuva. Futhi ngeke uthole izaziso uma izibuyekezo zivela."
"Ingabe ngempela ufuna ukukhipha le-akhawunti? Ukukukhipha kuzosusa yonke imiyalezo yayo, othintana nabo, neminye imininingo esuka kudivayisi!"
